Don't Leave Our Home! - Ludum Dare 23 - by EdiiKnorand

to compile:
$ make

to clear:
$ make clean

Z fires. 
X leaves/grabs the world.
Arrows moves.

The hitboxes are very stranges.

Made in a Linux and using SDL.
You can find it here: https://github.com/epc09/ld23

Kvisle made a Windows port: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/1287557/dontleave.zip (this has some bugs)

Thank you!
